creator: Octoze Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Camu - Staff App is meant for the Teaching and Administrative users of the "Camu. Your Campus" platform.

[IMPORTANT NOTE: The Camu app is meant for the users of Camu platform. If you are not a user of Camu platform, the download may not useful to you]

Camu platform provides a comprehensive ERP solutions designed for Education. Right from the admissions to the Alumni, Camu suits verity of Educational Institutes ranging from Schools to Multi campus Universities.

Camu App makes it easy to run a paperless classroom administration and ZERO data entry to manage day to day activities.

If you have any questions, please get in touch with us at support@octoze.com
